data.description: This charming home that's a perfect blend of modern comforts and rural tranquility is ready for its new owners. With 1,872 square feet of living space on a spacious 1.57-acre lot, this property offers ample room for you to enjoy the beauty of nature and the comforts of home.This cozy residence features three bedrooms, offering plenty of space for your family or guests. The two full baths ensure convenience, with one featuring a relaxing jetted tub, ideal for unwinding after a long day while viewing the beautiful colors of fall from the window. One of the standout features of this property is the two-car garage with a loft upstairs, presenting a unique opportunity for expansion. This versatile loft space could easily be transformed into a room that could be rented, generating additional income or providing a private retreat for your hobbies and interests.The main level of the home boasts a spacious kitchen and dining room, perfect for hosting family gatherings and creating lasting memories. You'll also appreciate the convenience of a main-level laundry area, making daily chores a breeze.The 1.57-acre lot provides plenty of space for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the peaceful surroundings. Located in Diamond, Ohio, this home offers the perfect balance between rural serenity and modern convenience, making it an ideal place to call home. Don't miss the opportunity to make this property your own and enjoy the best of both worlds. Schedule to see this today !
